headline: Corteva Q3: Lower Commodity And Raw Material Costs Ahead, Potential Margin Expansion
summary: Corteva's Q3 results showed weak growth in Latin America, but benefits from raw material cost deflation. Read why I reiterate a Buy rating for CTVA stock.
